author: Frank Corder
title: Change the #MSflag rally held at Mississippi Capitol
text: Change the #MSflag rally held at Mississippi Capitol Hundreds rally against Confederate sign on Mississippi flag About 400 people participated in a change-the-flag rally outside the Mississippi Capitol. No alternative design was proposed, but rally leaders said the flag is racially divisive. Sunherald
